OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer Jack
OL,7,FAbbey
OL,9,FThe annual rate of food inflation
OL,10,Fcould rise to up to 12% in 2026,
OL,11,Fmostly as a result of the energy
OL,12,Fcrisis spiked by the war in the Middle
OL,13,FEast, ITV News has been told.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
