OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775081465
OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FITV News has consulted academics at
OL,7,FThe Food Systems Institute at The
OL,8,FUniversity of Nottingham, Bournemouth
OL,9,FUniversity and the University of
OL,10,FExeter, two of whom have been advising
OL,11,Fthe government's Department of
OL,12,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs on
OL,13,Fhow to model the impact of energy
OL,14,Fprices on the retail price of food in
OL,15,Fthe current situation.
OL,17,FThe calculations were made on the
OL,18,Fbasis of energy prices remaining high
OL,19,Fat 50% above pre-war levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
