OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775081465
OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FAny prices rises, they emphasise,
OL,7,Fdepend hugely on the duration of the
OL,8,Fconflict and the levels of damage and
OL,9,Fdisruption to energy infrastructure in
OL,10,Fthe region.
OL,12,FPaul Wilson, Professor of Agricultural
OL,13,FEconomics at the University of
OL,14,FNottingham said, "We would expect some
OL,15,Fprices to move more or less
OL,16,Fimmediately, although the full effect
OL,17,Fwill unwind over the next 12-18 months.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
