OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Even if the war ended tomorrow we
OL,12,Fwould expect food prices to rise over
OL,13,Fthe medium term owing to current
OL,14,Fdisruption."
OL,16,FIn the aftermath of the war in Ukraine
OL,17,F- the last time we experienced an
OL,18,Fenergy shock - food price inflation
OL,19,Fpeaked at 19.2%.
OL,26,@vD@LO]
