OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FThat was exacerbated by a shortage of
OL,7,Fgrain which couldn't leave Ukraine,
OL,8,Fone of the world's biggest producers
OL,9,Fof the crop.
OL,11,FFood prices rose by 3.2% in year to
OL,12,FFebruary 2026 as the industry
OL,13,Fcontended with higher packaging costs
OL,14,Fdue to new regulations, the employers
OL,15,FNational Insurance hike, and an
OL,16,Fincreased minimum wage.
OL,18,FThat was higher than the overall rate
OL,19,Fof headline inflation of 3.0%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
