OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FEnergy is one of the most important
OL,7,Fdeterminants of food prices. It's
OL,8,Frequired in almost all stages of food
OL,9,Fproduction including heating,
OL,10,Frefrigeration, processing, packaging
OL,11,Fand transport.
OL,13,FNearly a third (30%) of the world's
OL,14,Fenergy usage is dedicated to food
OL,15,Fproduction.
OL,17,FExperts say all types of food will be
OL,18,Fimpacted but inflation of goods with
OL,19,Fshorter production times and those
OL,20,Fwhich require intensive energy inputs
OL,21,Fwill be felt earliest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
