OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FAmongst the first foods expected to
OL,7,Fexperience price rises are energy
OL,8,Fintensive horticultural products like
OL,9,Fcucumbers and tomatoes, which require
OL,10,Fheated greenhouses to grow.
OL,12,FOther candidates for inflation in the
OL,13,Fshort-term include heavily processed
OL,14,Ffoods like crisps and chocolate as
OL,15,Fwell as imported fruits and goods like
OL,16,Ftea and coffee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
