OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FInflation is likely to take longer to
OL,7,Ffeed through into grains like rice and
OL,8,Fwheat (the key ingredient in bread and
OL,9,Fpasta) because the crops take longer
OL,10,Fto grow, and much of the fertiliser
OL,11,Frequired for current crops will
OL,12,Falready have been bought.
OL,14,FMeats like lamb and beef are likely to
OL,15,Fbe the last foods impacted by rising
OL,16,Fprices because of how long the animals
OL,17,Ftake to raise - but they are not
OL,18,Fimmune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
