OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,FAcross the broad range of these
OL,7,Fproducts, increased transportation
OL,8,Fcosts amid a global shortage of diesel
OL,9,Fwill add to food inflation. A problem
OL,10,Fmade worse by Britain's reliance on
OL,11,Fimported food.
OL,13,FProfessor Emeritus Tim Lang, of City
OL,14,FSt George's University of London said:
OL,15,F"Britain is more exposed than other
OL,16,Fcountries because we have chosen not
OL,17,Fto produce very much food.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
