OL,3,CUK food inflation could hit 'double
OL,4,Cdigits' due to war in Iran
OL,6,F"We had to do it in World War II and
OL,7,Fwe then rebuilt agriculture up to
OL,8,Fabout 80%, 82% by the mid-1980s, and
OL,9,Fit's been slowly declining ever since.
OL,11,F"It depends how you calculate it,
OL,12,Fwe're maybe 50% to 60% self-reliant at
OL,13,Fthe moment. That means 40% not. That's
OL,14,Fa heck of a lot of food."
OL,16,FFood inflation can be particularly
OL,17,Fdamaging as it is felt
OL,18,Fdisproportionately by those on the
OL,19,Flowest incomes who spend a higher
OL,20,Fshare of their money on food than
OL,21,Fthose better off.
